      <title>BP首席执行官认为利润失利后的薪水削减30％，Elliott干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/bp-ceo-sees-pay-cut-30-after-profit-miss-elliott-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP PLC首席执行官Murray Auchincloss的总薪酬在2024年下跌至536万英镑（691万美元），比上一年比上一年低约30％，此前能源巨头的利润令人失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/bp-ceo-sees-pay-cut-30-after-profit-miss-elliott-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
